{"tid":958903,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"防彈少年團BTS踩宗教禁忌 紀錄片遭俄國禁播","createTime":"2018-12-28T07:51:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T08:39:23.000Z","uid":74065,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e061a22e4912ea285babae8bf5046fee76649f86","tid":958903,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T07:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/ent/page/800/2018/12/28/phpCx2Cy6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2Fent%2Fpage%2F800%2F2018%2F12%2F28%2FphpCx2Cy6.jpg&h=d9d05ea0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>防彈少年團遭信奉伊斯蘭教的激進份子質疑性向。（翻攝自韓網）</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n〔娛樂頻道／綜合報導〕南韓人氣男團防彈少年團（BTS）出道4年，人氣席捲全球，明年將推出第2部紀錄片《LOVE YOURSELF IN SEOUL》，近來卻傳出在俄羅斯遭禁播。<br />\n<br />\n防彈少年團巡演紀錄片《LOVE YOURSELF IN SEOUL》1月26日將在各地上映，位於俄羅斯南部的達吉斯坦共和國首都馬哈奇卡拉20日開始售票，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>當地信奉伊斯蘭教的激進份子提出抗議（伊斯蘭教中同性戀者是不被接受並認定為有罪的），認為防彈成員曾公開力挺同志，此舉有違宗教理念，質疑起7成員性向</strong></span>，甚至還在Instagram以「我們必須阻止同性戀團體BTS不道德的行為」，強烈反對紀錄片上映。戲院事後緊急將紀錄片宣傳海報撤下，並取消上映。<br />\n<br />\n仆街啦今次 JHOPE同我玩射精玩大左<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938cac59ff19c594981cea6a350e1a1c21f8c18c","tid":958903,"uid":213300,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T07:54:05.000Z","msg":"收聲啦傻鳩<br />\n佢好男仔嚟㗎"},{"pid":"5060a6c2280aff9ae7c2b95a390142bd51bf1665","tid":958903,"uid":46435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T07:57:41.000Z","msg":"V仔同我射精比我搞大左"},{"pid":"5eede00e87d0b09a992a89bd5fb606546fa7a16f","tid":958903,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"938cac59ff19c594981cea6a350e1a1c21f8c18c","tid":958903,"uid":213300,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":